<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 03:33:25 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>亚洲股市下跌，长期国债将迎来一年来最糟糕的一周</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-13/</link><description>亚洲股市周五下跌，原因是美元走强导致风险情绪脆弱，而随着美国 2025 年大幅降息的预期消退，长期国债收益率有望创下今年最大单周涨幅。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 02:44:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>墨西哥参议院批准应用程序驱动程序的工作福利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexican-senate-approves-work-benefits-app-drivers-2024-12-13/</link><description>墨西哥参议院周四批准了一项改革，以改善滴滴、Rappi 和 Uber 等网约车和送货服务司机的工作条件，确保他们获得社会保障和圣诞奖金等福利。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 02:08:27 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/mexican-senate-approves-work-benefits-app-drivers-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>油价因 2025 年供应过剩预测而小幅走低，但周度将录得涨幅</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-edges-lower-2025-supply-surplus-forecast-set-notch-weekly-gain-2024-12-13/</link><description>周五油价小幅走低，因投资者关注供应充足的预测，并摆脱了中国刺激措施明年需求增加的预期，同时关注美联储下周再次降息。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 02:04:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/oil-edges-lower-2025-supply-surplus-forecast-set-notch-weekly-gain-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国打破对可能举行演习的沉默，称对台独活动不会手软</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/breaking-silence-possible-drills-china-says-will-not-be-soft-taiwan-independence-2024-12-13/</link><description>中国国防部周五打破了对台湾周边几天军事活动的沉默，称是否举行演习由中国决定，军队在打击分裂势力的过程中“不会缺席”。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 01:43:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/breaking-silence-possible-drills-china-says-will-not-be-soft-taiwan-independence-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>官方媒体报道，中国因受贿罪判处前国家足球队主帅20年有期徒刑</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/china-sentences-former-national-soccer-coach-20-years-prison-bribery-state-media-2024-12-13/</link><description>中国官方媒体周五报道，中国前国家足球队主教练李铁因受贿罪被判处 20 年有期徒刑。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 01:29:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/soccer/china-sentences-former-national-soccer-coach-20-years-prison-bribery-state-media-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国表示将“根据斗争形势”决定在台湾周边举行军事演习</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-will-decide-hold-military-exercises-around-taiwan-according-situation-2024-12-13/</link><description>中国周五表示，将“根据自身需要和斗争形势”决定是否举行军事演习，以应对台湾总统赖清德最近访美。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 01:24:08 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-will-decide-hold-military-exercises-around-taiwan-according-situation-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国称菲律宾在美国支持下在南海“挑衅”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippines-has-provoked-trouble-south-china-sea-with-us-backing-2024-12-13/</link><description>中国周五指责菲律宾在美国的支持下在南海“挑衅”，一周前北京和马尼拉就争议海域发生的新对抗相互指责。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 01:09:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/china-says-philippines-has-provoked-trouble-south-china-sea-with-us-backing-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>全球电动汽车销量连续第三次创历史新高</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/global-ev-sales-hit-third-consecutive-record-high-2024-12-13/</link><description>市场研究公司 Rho Motion 周五公布的数据显示，11 月份全球纯电动和插电式混合动力汽车销量连续第七个月增长，同比增长 32%，连续第三次创下历史新高。</description><pubDate>Fri, 13 Dec 2024 00:04:13 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/global-ev-sales-hit-third-consecutive-record-high-2024-12-13/</guid></item><item><title>中国考虑人民币贬值，特朗普贸易顾问警告不要操纵汇率</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/trump-trade-adviser-warns-against-currency-manipulation-china-mulls-weaker-yuan-2024-12-12/</link><description>候任总统唐纳德·特朗普的高级贸易顾问周四告诉路透社，新政府不会“热衷于”中国操纵人民币的任何企图，回应路透社有关中国当局正在考虑允许人民币下一步贬值的报道。年。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 23:22:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/currencies/trump-trade-adviser-warns-against-currency-manipulation-china-mulls-weaker-yuan-2024-12-12/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国深化经济刺激，全球信号喜忧参半</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-12-12/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 21:48:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-12-12/</guid></item><item><title>美国声称朝鲜派工人到美国公司勒索钱财购买武器</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us-claims-north-korea-put-workers-us-companies-extort-money-weapons-2024-12-12/</link><description>美国周四悬赏 500 万美元，奖励有关一项涉嫌计划的信息，在该计划中，朝鲜技术工人在毫无戒心的美国公司找到工作，然后窃取他们的商业机密以换取赎金，所得收益用于资助平壤的武器计划。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 21:07:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us-claims-north-korea-put-workers-us-companies-extort-money-weapons-2024-12-12/</guid></item><item><title>中国承诺增加债务、降息以应对特朗普的关税威胁</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-pledges-more-debt-rate-cuts-counter-trumps-tariff-threats-2024-12-12/</link><description>中国周四承诺增加预算赤字、发行更多债务并放松货币政策，以保持稳定的经济增长率，以应对唐纳德·特朗普重返白宫后与美国的贸易紧张局势加剧。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 15:09:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-pledges-more-debt-rate-cuts-counter-trumps-tariff-threats-2024-12-12/</guid></item><item><title>特朗普邀请中国习近平出席就职典礼，专家称其为政治戏剧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-invites-chinas-xi-other-world-leaders-inauguration-2024-12-12/</link><description>特朗普过渡事务发言人周四表示，美国当选总统唐纳德·特朗普已邀请中国国家主席习近平和其他外国领导人参加下个月在华盛顿举行的就职典礼，但专家表示习近平不太可能出席。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 13:37:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/trump-invites-chinas-xi-other-world-leaders-inauguration-2024-12-12/</guid></item><item><title>英伟达否认将削减对中国供应的传言</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-denies-rumours-it-will-cut-supplies-china-2024-12-12/</link><description>英伟达在中国社交媒体上发布的一篇帖子称，最近社交媒体上声称该公司将削减对中国供应的帖子是虚假的。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 11:15:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/nvidia-denies-rumours-it-will-cut-supplies-china-2024-12-12/</guid></item><item><title>香港前民主派立法会议员等七人因 2019 年暴徒袭击后发生骚乱而被定罪</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-ex-democratic-lawmaker-convicted-rioting-after-2019-mob-attack-2024-12-12/</link><description>周四，香港一家法院以骚乱罪判处著名前民主派议员林卓廷有罪，此前他在 2019 年 7 月民主抗议活动最激烈的时候遭到白衬衫暴徒的袭击。</description><pubDate>Thu, 12 Dec 2024 10:17:50 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/hong-kong-ex-democratic-lawmaker-convicted-rioting-after-2019-mob-attack-2024-12-12/</guid></item></channel></rss>